1.启动 keycloak
	G:\keycloak-2.1.0.CR1\bin>standalone.bat -Djboss.socket.binding.port-offset=100
	
2.启动 WildFly
	F:\wildfly-10.0.0.Final\bin>standalone.bat
	
3.部署
	1).F:\kunlun\kunlun-identity>mvn clean wildfly:deploy
	成功后可登录。。有弹框
	2).创建client
		登录http://localhost:8180/auth/admin/
		copy至wildfly服务的standalone.xml：
		<secure-deployment name="kunlun-identity.war">
			<realm>demo</realm>
			<realm-public-key></realm-public-key>
			<auth-server-url>http://localhost:8180/auth</auth-server-url>
			<public-client>true</public-client>
			<ssl-required>EXTERNAL</ssl-required>
			<resource>kunlun-identity</resource>
		</secure-deployment>
		重启服务：F:\wildfly-10.0.0.Final\bin>standalone.bat
4.登录
	http://localhost:8180/auth/realms/的用户：
	用户名：chris.zhao@shijinet.com.cn
	密码：123
	用已创建好的用户登录http://localhost:8080/kunlun-identity/
